 "blurb": "Survival Hunter is a raid multiplier: Expose Weakness procs grant the whole melee/hunter core attack power scaled off your agility. Personal DPS is the lowest of the three trees; the raid total says otherwise, and the gear list stacks agility beyond what any other hunter would. This Phase 5 snapshot aggregates 195 top DPS parses from Sunwell Plateau; the highest-consensus pick is Gronnstalker's Bracers at 94% usage.",
